  <section>
    <h2>Accessibility</h2>

    <h3>ARIA Attributes</h3>
    <p>The component automatically applies ARIA attributes for accessibility:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><code>aria-expanded</code> on each summary indicates open/closed state</li>
      <li><code>aria-controls</code> links summaries to their panels</li>
      <li><code>aria-labelledby</code> links panels back to their summaries</li>
      <li><code>role="region"</code> on panels for landmark navigation</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Screen Reader Announcements</h3>
    <p>Screen readers will announce the expanded/collapsed state when panels are toggled. The keyboard navigation allows users to move between headers without expanding panels.</p>

    <h3>Focus Management</h3>
    <p>Focus remains on the summary element when toggling, and arrow key navigation moves focus between summaries without changing the open state.</p>
  </section>

